isible-xs list-languages"> <select class="styled-language-select i-arrow-down-after redirection-select"><option value="https://www.icrc.org/it" selected="selected">IT</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/en">EN</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/fr">FR</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/es">ES</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/pt">PT</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/zh">ZH</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/ar">AR</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/ru">RU</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/de">DE</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/en/languages">Altro</option> </select></div></div></div></div></header></div><div class="fill section-first-main"><div class="video-section"><div class="video-wrapper responsive-video-container video-available"> <video data-keepplaying data-autoplay loop muted poster="https://www.icrc.org/sites/default/files/styles/special_page_image/public/homepage_files/icrc-car-syria_1.jpg?itok=sydI4NeT"> <source data-src="https://www.icrc.org/sites/default/files/homepage_files/what-we-do-video_0.mp4" type="video/mp4" /> </video><div class="image"> <img src="https://www.icrc.org/sites/default/files/styles/special_page_image/public/homepage_files/icrc-car-syria_1.jpg?itok=sydI4NeT" alt="icrc-car-syria"/></div><div class="video-text-wrapper"><div class="video-text"> <a href="/it/what-we-do/video" class="lightbox-embed-video youtube"><span class="thumbnail-video-button"></span></a><div class="main-text">Sul terreno in oltre 90 paesi - neutrali, imparziali e indipendenti - siamo il Comitato internazionale della Croce Rossa</div></div></div></div></div><div class="text-section"><div class="container fill"><div class="row fill"><div class="text-wrapper-outer fill"><div class="text-wrapper"><div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 text-block"> <a class="title-text" href="https://www.icrc.org/it/chi-siamo" class="">Chi siamo</a><div class="red-divider"></div><div class="sub-text"><p>Il CICR protegge e aiuta le vittime di conflitti armati e promuove il rispetto del diritto internazionale umanitario. Qui troverete maggiori informazioni su chi siamo.</p></div></div><div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 text-block"> <a class="title-text" href="https://www.icrc.org/en/who-we-are/jobs" class="">Lavorare con noi</a><div class="red-divider"></div><div class="sub-text"><p>Ha una forte motivazione umanitaria? Troverà ulteriori informazioni su come lavorare dall'ICRC. (link in inglese)</p></div></div><div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 text-block"> <a class="title-text" href="https://www.icrc.org/it/sosteneteci" class="">Sostienici</a><div class="red-divider"></div><div class="sub-text"><p>Aiuti le famiglie colpite da conflitti armati in tutte le regioni del mondo.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section> <section class="custom-block-list section fp-normal-scroll fp-auto-height clear ss" id="custom-block-list"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-xs-12"><div class="custom-block"> <a href="https://issuu.com/icrc1/docs/icrc_magazine_it" tabindex="-1"><div class="image"> <img src="https://www.icrc.org/sites/default/files/styles/home_custom_block/public/home_custom_block/image/02.jpg?itok=xax2Z8dk" alt="Il CICR In Azione" /></div> </a><div class="content-wrapper"><div class="content"><h2>Il CICR In Azione</h2><div class="text"><p>Venite a scoprire come le attività del CICR aiutano me, le donne e i bambini intrappolati nei conflitti del mondo.</p></div> <a href="https://issuu.com/icrc1/docs/icrc_magazine_it" class="link">Leggete la nostra rivista</a></div></div></div></div></div></div></section></div></div><footer class="clear"> <nav class="footer-nav clear"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-md-3"><div class="hidden-xs hidden-sm"><h2>Il lavoro del CICR</h2><div><p>Il CICR protegge e aiuta le vittime di conflitti armati e promuove il rispetto del diritto internazionale umanitario. Qui troverete maggiori informazioni su <a href="https://www.icrc.org/it/chi-siamo">chi siamo</a>.</p></div></div><div class="hidden-md hidden-lg"><h2>Iscrivetevi alla newsletter del CICR</h2><div><form action="https://www.icrc.org/it/newsletter" method="get" novalidate="novalidate" class="footer-newsletter-form"> <button type="submit">Abbonarsi</button><div class="input-wrapper"> <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Indirizzo e-mail"></div></form></div></div></div><div class="col-md-2"><h2>Sezioni</h2><div class="hidden-xs hidden-sm"><ul><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/it/chi-siamo">Chi siamo</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/it/where-we-work">Dove lavoriamo</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/it/sosteneteci">Sosteneteci</a></li></ul></div><div class="hidden-md hidden-lg"><div class="footer-dropdown"> <button>...<span class="button-icon i-arrow-down"></span></button><div class="footer-dropdown-content"><ul><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/it/chi-siamo">Chi siamo</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/it/where-we-work">Dove lavoriamo</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/it/sosteneteci">Sosteneteci</a></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class="col-md-3"></div><div class="col-md-4"><div class="hidden-xs hidden-sm"><h2>Iscrivetevi alla newsletter del CICR</h2><div><form action="https://www.icrc.org/it/newsletter" method="get" novalidate="novalidate" class="footer-newsletter-form"> <button type="submit">Abbonarsi</button><div class="input-wrapper"> <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Indirizzo e-mail"></div></form></div></div><div class="blog-list"><h2>ICRC Blogs</h2><div><div class="footer-dropdown"> <button>...<span class="button-icon i-arrow-down"></span></button><div class="footer-dropdown-content"><ul><li> <a href="http://intercrossblog.icrc.org/" target="_blank">Washington</a></li><li> <a href="http://blogs.icrc.org/ilot/" target="_blank">Israel and the occupied territories</a></li><li> <a href="http://blogs.icrc.org/new-de